===Noun===
'''jelly bean''' (''Plural:'' '''jelly beans''')

#A small flavorful chewy candy with a jelly like center, composed of [[sugar]], flavoring, coloring and sometimes [[starch]] or other thickener.  In shape resembling a bean, usually brightly colored and available in a great variety of flavors.

